Package org.openlcb.swing.memconfig Description

Swing JPanels for doing direct manipulation via the Memory Configuration Protocol

This is not intended as a base for production implementations, but rather a convenient example of implementing of OpenLCB protocols.

The various "Pane" classes implement independent pieces that can be arranged as needed. For example, a simple configuration window doesn't need to show the description information pane.
